{0 'Chrysler Corp said it and RegieNationale des Usines Renault <RENA.PA> agreed to set May 5 asthe new target date when Chrysler aimed at reaching adefinitive agreement for Chrysler for acquire American MotorsCorp. AMC is 46.1 pct owned by Renault. The two companies originally had targeted April 23 ascompletion date for reaching a definitive agreement. Chrysler, which signed a letter of intent on March 9 toacquire AMC, said \"considerable progress has been made, but anumber of issues remain to be resolved.\" Reuter',1 ACQ}
